":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions","text":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox\/b\/6578e5\/t\/3dd013a529"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"type":"par